{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"63314-a-minha-professora","title":"A Minha Professora","description":"How much do you love your teacher?","language":"Portuguese","langCode":"pt","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Teresa  Sousa","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Jesse Pietersen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/63314-a-minha-professora"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/92778/size3/c46013ed18e3a87b20c3f493722c20f2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/92778/size6/c46013ed18e3a87b20c3f493722c20f2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89415/size6/1a9b9c9881cf211d74fe3904a30682c9.jpg","text":"Eu gosto muito da minha professora.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89416/size6/28ffd051707553b05328fd91d2fdf2d3.jpg","text":"Ela é bonita. Ela é uma boa professora. Ela é bondosa e paciente.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89417/size6/695fd36356f3b9b9736d2581d41d3407.jpg","text":"Ela trançou muito bem o cabelo dela.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89418/size6/ace424dfb60c0019738b9a16f1323227.jpg","text":"Ela pôs missangas coloridas no cabelo dela.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89419/size6/e1e51ec8f931503eb312887940b8fc96.jpg","text":"As missangas dela são verdes, brancas, vermelhas e amarelas.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89420/size6/ce437f3de0867366119a9db0c1d03076.jpg","text":"Mãe, por favor, podes trançar o meu cabelo como o da minha professora?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89421/size6/cab5a86238a97413ccd67594dd5e4d37.jpg","text":"Quando eu for mais velha também vou por missangas no meu cabelo.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89422/size6/f1f2fb84ae4c3c1d0c5649a17de2d794.jpg","text":"Vou crescer e ser igual à minha professora!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":75}}